    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is ideal for someone looking for a major restoration project or a reliable source of spare parts. The exterior shows significant wear, including several large dents, rust spots on the wheel arches, and clear coat failure across the hood and roof. Mechanically, the engine requires a complete overhaul and the transmission is currently slipping. The interior has seen better days, with torn upholstery and some non-functional electronics. Please expect to tow this vehicle away, as it is not currently in roadworthy condition.",
